---
title: "The Blues win the Stanley Cup"
output: html_document
---

The Blues won their first **Stanley Cup** in 2019. The Stanley Cup is the trophy the champions of the NHL get. It took the Blues 52 years to win the trophy, the longest any team has had to win their first title. The blues were coapchec by Craig Berube and Captained by Defenseman Alex Pietrangelo. 
